-------------------------
Logistical Mission Strategy Generator - In collaboration with Fleets-Online
-------------------------
Description
This Knowledge-Based Engineering application can be used to generate the best strategy for logistical problems
in for example the agricultural, construction and transportation industries. The application uses fleet data
provided by the user and iterates over possible strategies to come up with a winning strategy based on one or more
of the following goals: Time, Cost and/or Emissions (CO2 + NOx).
-------------------------
Usage
To run the application, run the file 'main.py'. This file will instantiate the root object, called
'MissionStrategyApp'. A ParaPy GUI will open, which contains buttons to run the mission generator, visualize
different outputs and alter the used data.
-------------------------
Dependencies
---
APIs
The FleetsOnline API is used by sending requests to 'https://api.v2.deepdigital.org', which requires a FleetsOnline
account for authentication.
The OpenRouteService API is used, which requires an ORS account for authentication.
---
Libraries
parapy v1.15.1
kbeutils v1.0
routingpy v1.3.1
numpy v2.4.6
requests v2.34.2
reportlab v4.5.1
